RawLine: ITEM_700011_Tip,一種茶，名為千杯不醉。這茶在沖泡時，一股淡若無味的酒香慢慢地飄起來，酒香陣陣，沁人心脾，未飲先如醉。當入口後，齒留香，如美酒般味醇勁足，但不使人醉。,一种茶，名为千杯不醉。这茶在冲泡时，一股淡若无味的酒香慢慢地飘起来，酒香阵阵，沁人心脾，未饮先如醉。当入口后，齿留香，如美酒般味醇劲足，但不使人醉。

Items.mt: There is a kind of tea called "A Thousand Cups of Intoxication". When this tea is brewed, a tasteless fragrance of wine slowly floats up, and the fragrance of wine is so refreshing that it makes you feel drunk before you drink it. When the mouth, the teeth remain fragrant, like a fine wine taste mellow and strong enough, but not make people drunk.
